INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (2,1,'2011-05-04 07:49:56','2011-05-04 07:49:56','This is an example page. It\'s different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:\n\n<blockquote>Hi there! I\'m a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my blog. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like pi&#241;a coladas. (And gettin\' caught in the rain.)</blockquote>\n\n...or something like this:\n\n<blockquote>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickies to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</blockquote>\n\nAs a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href=\"http://w467171.s182.ufhosted.com/wp-admin/\">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!','Sample Page','','publish','open','open','','sample-page','','','2011-05-04 07:49:56','2011-05-04 07:49:56','',0,'http://w467171.s182.ufhosted.com/?page_id=2',0,'page','',0),(381,1,'2011-11-13 17:33:58','2011-11-13 09:33:58','<p class=\"course-info\">2011年12月19 上海</p>\r\n<p class=\"teacher\">讲师：Gojko Adzic</p>\r\n<p class=\"classroom\">地点：上海，舜元国际，江苏路398号</p>\r\n<!--more-->\r\n<p class=\"value\">价格：RMB 1000元每位，提早报名或团队报名有优惠。</p>\r\n<p class=\"tel\">联系方式: Tel: 021-63809913</p>\r\n<p class=\"email\">Email: <a href=\"mailto:Service@ScrumChina.com\">Service@ScrumChina.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"text\">\r\n<h3>课程优势：</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>PMI PMP PDU &amp; ACP Contact Hours</li>\r\n	<li>全球知名的BDD/ATDD专家Gojko Adzic讲授</li>\r\n        <li>Gojko Adzic是2本BDD方面敏捷畅销书的作者</li>\r\n	<li>另有数位知名上海社区敏捷实践者现场支持</li>\r\n	<li>互动性和实操性强，千锤百炼的口碑课程，获广泛推荐</li>\r\n	<li>4星级的场地和服务</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>授课顾问：</h3>\r\n<div class=\"teacher-info\">\r\n<div class=\"teacher-pic\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-90\" title=\"Mr. Gojko Adzic\" src=\"http://w467171.s182.ufhosted.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/Vernon-150-170.jpg\" alt=\"Mr. Gojko Adzic\" width=\"150\" height=\"170\" /><span>Mr. Gojko Adzic</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"teacher-text\">\r\n\r\n<strong>Gojko Adzic from UK</strong>Gojko Adzic is a strategic software delivery consultant who works with ambitious teams to improve the quality of their software products and processes. He specialises in agile and lean quality improvement, in particular agile testing, specification by example and behaviour driven development.\r\nGojko is a frequent speaker at leading software development and testing conferences and runs the UK Agile Testing User Group.  \r\nOver the last eleven years, he has worked as a developer, architect, technical director and consultant on projects delivering financial and energy trading platforms, mobile positioning and e-commerce applications, online gaming and complex configuration management systems.\r\nHe is the author of 2 best-selling books: Specification by Example & Bridging the Communication Gap, as well as Test Driven .NET Development with FitNesse and The Secret Ninja Cucumber Scrolls. </p></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>课程主要模块：</h3>\r\n<ul class=\"summary\">\r\n	<li>Exposing Problems with Imperative Requirements；</li>\r\n	<li>Communicating with Examples；</li>\r\n	<li>What Makes a Good Specification with Examples/Acceptance Tests；</li>\r\n	<li>Key Process Patterns；</li>\r\n<div class=\"clear\"></div> \r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>课程概要：</h3>\r\n“From User Stories to Acceptance Tests – Specification by Example/BDD Fundamentals” （从用户故事到接受测试－实例化需求分析／行为驱动开发基础工作坊）is an interactive training workshop, aimed at providing skills to bridge the communication gap between stakeholders and implementation teams, build quality into software from the start, design, develop and deliver systems fit for purpose by applying emerging collaborative requirements management, specification and testing practices in agile and lean processes.\r\n\r\nThe workshop is based on Gojko Adzic\'s books Bridging the Communication Gap and Specification by Example, as well as years of practical experience with many teams in different contexts. It is very interactive and practical, focused on providing participants with first-hand real world experience and aimed at cross-functional training groups of business analysts, product owners, developers and testers.\r\n\r\n<h3>报名咨询：</h3>\r\n<p class=\"tel\">Tel: 021-63809913</p>\r\n<p class=\"email\">Email: <a href=\"mailto:Service@ScrumChina.com\">Service@ScrumChina.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n</div>','From User Stories to Acceptance Tests–Specification by Example/BDD Fundamentals 从用户故事到接受测试－实例化需求分析／行为驱动开发基础工作坊','','inherit','open','open','','374-revision-4','','','2011-11-13 17:33:58','2011-11-13 09:33:58','',374,'http://www.uperform.cn/uncategorized/374-revision-4',0,'revision','',0),(108,1,'2011-08-13 13:00:11','2011-08-13 13:00:11','<p class=\"course-info\">3月4日-3月5日 北京</p>\r\n<p class=\"teacher\">讲师：Vernon Stinebaker 史文林 &amp; 李国彪</p>\r\n<p class=\"classroom\">地点：北京，丽亭华苑, 知春路25号</p>\r\n<!--more-->\r\n<p class=\"value\">课程价值: RMB 7000</p>\r\n<p class=\"tel\">联系方式: Tel: 010-85679828, 021-63809913</p>\r\n<p class=\"email\">Email: <a href=\"mailto:Service@ScrumChina.com\">Service@ScrumChina.com</a></p>\r\n<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"text\">\r\n<p>简要课程大纲：课程主要涉及以下主题：</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>敏捷思维及原则；</li>  \r\n<li>与传统项目管理的比较；</li> \r\n<li>Scrum过程的特征；</li> \r\n<li>商业价值驱动与交付；</li> \r\n<li>Scrum框架（角色、会议仪式、工件）；</li> \r\n<li>Scrum模拟游戏；</li> \r\n<li>敏捷项目跟踪及绩效；</li> \r\n<li>用户故事与敏捷需求；</li> \r\n<li>敏捷团队及项目的扩展；</li> \r\n<li>敏捷估算和发布规划；</li> \r\n<li>ScrumMaster的探讨 </li> \r\n</ul>\r\n<p>两位海内外实战经验丰富的资深敏捷顾问提供超高性价比的培训。两天的课程将分散穿插五分钟的简短练习和案例研究。以上每个主题所花费的时间将视上课人员的组成情况及人们对特定领域的兴趣而调整。 </p>\r\n<p>详细课程大纲: 请联系我们获取大纲</p>\r\n<p>双证书: 课程结束时，每位学员将获得Scrum Alliance颁发的Certified ScrumMaster证书及2年的联盟会员资格，同时获得PMI的PDU学分。课程结束后学员将获得课程电子版材料。该次课同时获赠我们参与翻译的中文版《用户故事与敏捷方法》一书。</p>\r\n</div>','ScrumMaster 中文认证培训','','inherit','open','open','','8-revision-3','','','2011-08-13 13:00:11','2011-08-13 13:00:11','',8,'http://w467171.s182.ufhosted.com/uncategorized/8-revision-3',0,'revision','',0),(8,1,'2011-05-09 15:23:08','2011-05-09 15:23:08','<p class=\"course-info\">2011年9月18－19 上海 (Done!)</p>\r\n<p class=\"teacher\">讲师：Vernon Stinebaker 史文林，李国彪</p>\r\n<p class=\"classroom\">地点：上海，浦东陆家嘴软件园</p>\r\n<!--more-->\r\n<p class=\"value\">价格：RMB 7000元每位，提早报名或团队报名有优惠。</p>\r\n<p class=\"tel\">联系方式: Tel: 021-63809913</p>\r\n<p class=\"email\">Email: <a href=\"mailto:Service@ScrumChina.com\">Service@ScrumChina.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"text\">\r\n<h3>课程优势：</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Scrum联盟 ScrumMaster CSM认证 及 PMI PMP PDU &amp; ACP Contact Hours</li>\r\n	<li>能讲流利中文的知名老外敏捷专家Vernon讲授</li>\r\n	<li>知名Scrum教练李国彪先生现场支持</li>\r\n	<li>互动性和实操性强，千锤百炼的口碑课程，获广泛推荐</li>\r\n	<li>4星级的场地和服务</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>授课顾问：</h3>\r\n<div class=\"teacher-info\">\r\n<div class=\"teacher-pic\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-90\" title=\"Vernon Stinebaker 史文林先生\" src=\"http://w467171.s182.ufhosted.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/Vernon-150-170.jpg\" alt=\"Vernon Stinebaker 史文林先生\" width=\"150\" height=\"170\" /><span>Vernon Stinebaker 史文林先生</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"teacher-text\">\r\n\r\n<strong>Vernon Stinebaker 史文林先生 CST （长居中国，来自美国）</strong>认证Scrum培训师，高级顾问，信息技术高管，教练，资深讲师。在中国已成功交付多次课程，均获得众多客户与学员的高度认可，主要客户包括HP、Sun、东软、Autodesk、海辉、2K Games、支付宝、Nokia、Virtuos 等知名企业。\r\n\r\n作为Perficient杭州的技术及运营总监，他的专长是敏捷方法（Scrum、FDD、XP等）、技术领导、软件开发、流程管理和再造、商务/运作绩效管理。他拥有20多年的信息技术产业经验，其中包括10多年在中国领导屡获殊荣的软件工程高层管理工作、IT及组织运营工作。从战略规划到团队组建，通过提供服务及持续的服务管理等业务发展的各个阶段施展经验与才干。在领导力、管理培训、技术、咨询和业务发展等发面均扮演成功的角色。除了敏捷，他也熟知传统过程方法，也是CMMi方面的专家。史先生可以用英文或流利中文授课及提供敏捷教练与辅导服务。</p></div>\r\n<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>课程主要内容概要：</h3>\r\n<ul class=\"summary\">\r\n	<li>敏捷思维与原则；</li>\r\n	<li>敏捷价值游戏；</li>\r\n	<li>Scrum特征；</li>\r\n	<li>Scrum框架；</li>