ous Integration\r\n\r\n<h3>课程主要内容：</h3>\r\n<ul class=\"summary\">\r\n	<li>3个迷你的Sprint演练；</li>\r\n	<li>敏捷工程技术环境；</li>\r\n	<li>开发人员在Scrum中的角色；</li>\r\n	<li>测试先行；</li>\r\n	<li>编写单元测试；</li>\r\n	<li>敏捷分析；</li>\r\n	<li>代码质量；</li>\r\n	<li>Scrum团队协作；</li>\r\n	<li>Scrum会议演练；</li>\r\n	<li>测试驱动开发；</li>\r\n	<li>敏捷架构；</li>\r\n	<li>敏捷设计；</li>\r\n	<li>重构；</li>\r\n        <li>经常集成和持续集成；</li>\r\n<div class=\"clear\"></div> \r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>证书及其他：</h3>\r\n课程结束后完成学分注册手续时，若学员已经拥有CSD另外2天的学分或者已经是CSM或者CSPO认证持有者，并通过我们的课后评估，学员可以向Scrum Alliance申请Certified Scrum Developer证书，同时获得PMI的ACP Contact Hours。每位学员获赠计划扑克。课程结束后学员将获得课程电子版材料。\r\n<h3>报名咨询及获取详细课程大纲：</h3>\r\n<p class=\"tel\">Tel: 021-63809913</p>\r\n<p class=\"email\">Email: <a href=\"mailto:Service@ScrumChina.com\">Service@ScrumChina.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n</div>','Certified Scrum Developer-CSD-Scrum开发者认证学分培训','','inherit','open','open','','389-revision-6','','','2011-11-14 16:54:20','2011-11-14 08:54:20','',389,'http://www.uperform.cn/uncategorized/389-revision-6',0,'revision','',0),(382,1,'2011-11-13 17:45:30','2011-11-13 09:45:30','','Gojko','','inherit','open','open','','gojko','','','2011-11-13 17:45:30','2011-11-13 09:45:30','',0,'http://www.uperform.cn/wp-content/uploads/2011/11/gojko.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(383,1,'2011-11-13 17:41:18','2011-11-13 09:41:18','<p class=\"course-info\">2011年12月19 上海</p>\r\n<p class=\"teacher\">讲师：Gojko Adzic</p>\r\n<p class=\"classroom\">地点：上海，舜元国际，江苏路398号</p>\r\n<!--more-->\r\n<p class=\"value\">价格：RMB 1000元每位，提早报名或团队报名有优惠。</p>\r\n<p class=\"tel\">联系方式: Tel: 021-63809913</p>\r\n<p class=\"email\">Email: <a href=\"mailto:Service@ScrumChina.com\">Service@ScrumChina.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"text\">\r\n<h3>课程优势：</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>PMI PMP PDU &amp; ACP Contact Hours</li>\r\n	<li>全球知名的BDD/ATDD专家Gojko Adzic讲授</li>\r\n        <li>Gojko Adzic是2本BDD方面敏捷畅销书的作者</li>\r\n	<li>另有数位知名上海社区敏捷实践者现场支持</li>\r\n	<li>互动性和实操性强，千锤百炼的口碑课程，获广泛推荐</li>\r\n	<li>4星级的场地和服务</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>授课顾问：</h3>\r\n<div clas