ko Adzic是2本BDD方面敏捷畅销书的作者(Specification by Example & Bridging the Communication Gap)</li>\r\n	<li>另有数位知名上海社区敏捷实践者现场支持</li>\r\n	<li>互动性和实操性强，千锤百炼的口碑课程，获广泛推荐</li>\r\n        <li>PMI PMP PDU &amp; ACP Contact Hours</li>\r\n	<li>4星级的场地和服务</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>授课顾问：</h3>\r\n<div class=\"teacher-info\">\r\n<div class=\"teacher-pic\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-90\" title=\"Mr. Gojko Adzic\" src=\"http://w467171.s182.ufhosted.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/11/gojko.png\" alt=\"Mr. Gojko Adzic\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /><span>Mr. Gojko Adzic</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"teacher-text\">\r\n\r\n<strong>Gojko Adzic from UK</strong>Gojko Adzic is a strategic software delivery consultant who works with ambitious teams to improve the quality of their software products and processes. He specialises in agile and lean quality improvement, in particular agile testing, specification by example and behaviour driven development.\r\nGojko is a frequent speaker at leading software development and testing conferences and runs the UK Agile Testing User Group.  \r\nOver the last eleven years, he has worked as a developer, architect, technical director and consultant on projects delivering financial and energy trading platforms, mobile positioning and e-commerce applications, online gaming and complex configuration management systems.\r\nHe is the author of 2 best-selling books: Specification by Example & Bridging the Communication Gap, as well as Test Driven .NET Development with FitNesse and The Secret Ninja Cucumber Scrolls. </p></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>课程主要模块：</h3>\r\n<ul class=\"summary\">\r\n	<li>Exposing Problems with Imperative Requirements；</li>\r\n	<li>Communicating with Examples；</li>\r\n	<li>What Makes a Good Specification with Examples/Acceptance Tests；</li>\r\n	<li>Key Process Patterns；</li>\r\n<div class=\"clear\"></div> \r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>课程概要：</h3>\r\n“From User Stories to Acceptance Tests – Specification by Example/BDD Fundamentals” （从用户故事到接受测试－实例化需求分析／行为驱动开发基础工作坊）is an interactive training workshop, aimed at providing skills to bridge the communication gap between stakeholders and implementation teams, build quality into software from the start, design, develop and deliver systems fit for purpose by applying emerging collaborative requirements management, specification and testing practices in agile and lean processes.\r\n\r\nThe workshop is based on Gojko Adzic\'s books Bridging the Communication Gap and Specification by Example, as well as years of practical experience with many teams in different contexts. It is very interactive and practical, focused on providing participants with first-hand real world experience and aimed at cross-functional training groups of business analysts, product owners, developers and testers.\r\n\r\n<h3>报名咨询：</h3>\r\n<p class=\"tel\">Tel: 021-63809913</p>\r\n<p class=\"email\">Email: <a href=\"mailto:Service@ScrumChina.com\">Service@ScrumChina.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n</div>','从用户故事到接受测试－实例化需求驱动开发基础工作坊 From User Stories to Acceptance Tests–Specification by Example/BDD Fundamentals','','inherit','open','open','','374-revision-9','','','2011-11-13 17:53:22','2011-11-13 09:53:22','',374,'http://www.uperform.cn/uncategorized/374-revision-9',0,'revision','',0),(118,1,'2011-08-30 14:46:17','2011-08-30 06:46:17','<ul class=\"quick-link\">\n<li><a href=\"#q1\">什么课程适合我（我们）？</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#q2\">Scrum联盟认证体系是怎样的？</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#q3\">你们的课程能否提供PMI的PDU？</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#q4\">公开班报名流程是怎样的？</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#q5\">能否提供发票，怎样支付学费？</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#q6\">内训是否可以提供认证？</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 class=\"question\" id=\"q1\">什么课程适合我（我们）？</h3>\n<p class=\"answer\">在我们的企业内训页面，我们尝试说明了每一个课程的面向对象，你可以访问该页面作详细参考。简单来说，ScrumMaster的认证或非认证课程（包括Scrum敏捷项目管理核心应用及Scrum概要课程）适合于绝大部分与开发项目相关的人员，包括管理层。这些课程是敏捷，特别是Scrum的核心基础培训。Product Owner认证或非认证课程适合于产品管理者、需求负责人及商业分析人员等。而用户故事、敏捷估算和规划适合于所有人员。管理层也可以考虑参加敏捷管理者概要短训。另外，开发人员可以在Scrum基础课的基础上参加CSD3天的敏捷技术实践课程，以及其他专题课程，例如TDD核心课和其他定制课程（如：单元测试，BDD，ATDD……）等。测试人员可以参加Scrum基础课和敏捷测试课程。</p>\n<h3 class=\"question\" id=\"q2\">Scrum联盟认证体系是怎样的？</h3>\n<h4>入门级认证：</h4>\n<p class=\"answer\">\n<strong>CSM</strong> (Certified ScrumMaster)，需要全程参与至少2天的CSM课程并完成网上自我评测。课程必须由CST讲授。\n<strong>CSPO</strong>（Certified Scrum Product Owner），需要全程参与至少2天的CSPO课程。课程必须由CST讲授。\n<strong>CSD</strong>（Certified Scrum Developer），需要参与一共不少于5天的具备CSD学分资格的课程。这些课程必须由Scrum联盟的REP提供。UPerform是国内首家获得REP资格的机构。5天中1天是Scrum Overview，另外1天的Scrum或者技术选修课，以及3天必修的敏捷技术实践课程。其中头2天可以由CSM课程代替。CSD认证资格由学员在满足5天学分条件后自行向Scrum联盟申请并通过审核，并支付认证费用。</p>\n<h4>中级认证：</h4>\n<p class=\"answer\"><strong>CSP</strong>（Certified Scrum Professional），申请该认证时申请人必须已经是CSM或CSPO或CSD，并已经有满一年的实际项目中应用Scrum的经验。在Scrum联盟网站下载申请表格，回答一系列问题，填好后向联盟提交，成功通过联盟的审核，并支付认证费用。请注意，此一年Scrum经验可以是入门级认证获得之前的经验。</p>\n<h4>高级认证：</h4>\n<p class=\"answer\"><strong>CST</strong>（Certified Scrum Trainer），需要经过很多的积累和成长。准备及申请详情请参考Scrum联盟网站。\n<strong>CSC</strong>（Certified Scrum Coach），需要经过很多的积累和成长。准备及申请详情请参考Scrum联盟网站。</p>\n<h3 class=\"question\" id=\"q3\">你们的课程能否提供PMI的PDU及ACP认证所需的学习小时？</h3>\n<p class=\"answer\">我们的大部分课程每天能向PMI申请获取7－8个PDU或者用于ACP的学习小时(。其中包括CSM，CSPO，Scrum核心应用，以及用户故事、敏捷估算规划等课程。我们会提供具体的指引以帮助PDU的申请。</p>\n<h3 class=\"question\" id=\"q4\">公开班报名流程</h3>\n<p class=\"answer\">咨询及索要报名表（请发邮件到<a href=\"mailto:Service@ScrumChina.Com\">Service@ScrumChina.Com</a>或随时致电021-63809913）——发回签名后的报名表（传真或扫描后发邮件）——支付报名费——寄送发票</p>\n<h3 class=\"question\" id=\"q5\">能否提供发票，怎样支付学费？</h3>\n<p class=\"answer\">可以提供正规发票。通过网上或线下银行转账或银行柜面存现支付报名费到优普丰公司账户，如下所示。转账时请注明报名人或者单位信息。若想支付到其他银行账户的客户，请联系我们以提供其他更加方便您的银行信息。<br/>\n开户行：上海银行愚园路支行\n银行账号：3164 1803 0002 50561\n账户名称：上海优普丰企业管理有限公司</p>\n<h3 class=\"question\" id=\"q6\">内训是否可以提供认证？</h3>\n<p class=\"answer\">可以的，主要看客户的需要及选择的培训师。</p>','FAQ','','inherit','open','open','','52-autosave','','','2011-08-30 14:46:17','2011-08-30 06:46:17','',52,'http://w467171.s182.ufhosted.com/uncategorized/52-autosave',0,'revision','',0),(119,1,'2011-08-13 11:40:15','2011-08-13 11:40:15','','FAQ','','inherit','open','open',''